# Operational Process Efficiency Tracker (OPET)

## Business Description
OPET is a web application for tracking operational process efficiency. It monitors task processing times, identifies bottlenecks, and analyzes resource utilization.

## Demo Login
- Username: admin
- Password: admin123

## Features
- Task management
- Dashboard with total tasks, completed tasks, average processing time
- Complete tasks and track duration
- Resource utilization monitoring
- Simple analytics (extendable with charts)

## Tech Stack
- Python 3.x + Flask
- SQLite Database
- Bootstrap 5

## Deployment Instructions
1. Clone repository:
```bash
git clone <repo_url>
cd OPET
